.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-DECODE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-decode \- decode a BOLT-11 invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-decode
.I bolt11
.SH DESCRIPTION
Decodes a BOLT-11 invoice via
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR decodepay
and returns a stable JSON subset:
.nf
{
  "amount_msat": <int>,
  "amount_sat": <int>,
  "description": "...",
  "payee": "<pubkey>",
  "payment_hash": "<hex>",
  "expiry": <seconds>,
  "created_at": <unix-ts>
}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Decode successful.
.TP
.B 5
Decode failed (invalid invoice or daemon unavailable).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-account-pay (1)
